Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/Uaemextop/echosmart

Package: echosmart-gateway
Architecture: arm64 amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: EchoSmart IoT Gateway for precision agriculture
 Complete gateway daemon for the EchoSmart IoT kit.
 Includes C++ binaries for sensor reading (DS18B20, DHT22, BH1750,
 soil moisture, MH-Z19C), system diagnostics, alert evaluation and
 data synchronisation with the cloud backend.
 .
 Designed to run on Raspberry Pi OS (arm64) as a systemd service.
